name: Handle OTP flow in signIn
requires: [S65-T02]

scope: |
  Extend signIn logic to handle multi-step auth:
  - result="ok" → store token, proceed
  - result="otp" → return to caller indicating OTP needed (authenticator)
  - result="mail" → return to caller indicating email code needed
  - result="wrong" → return error indicating wrong code
  Re-call signIn with otp field populated on second attempt.

files: [src/lib/api.ts]
